trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> class manages a collection of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> objects.

The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.#ctor" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> class.
The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object to add.

The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.Add(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl)" /> method adds a new <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object to the collection.

The index of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> at which the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object has been added.
<paramref name="control" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="control" />이 null 참조(Visual Basic의 경우 <see langword="Nothing" />)인 경우

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.AddRange(*)" /> method adds a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> object to the current collection.
An array of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> objects to add to the collection.

The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.AddRange(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl[])" /> method adds an array of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> objects to the collection.
<paramref name="controls" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="controls" />이 null 참조(Visual Basic의 경우 <see langword="Nothing" />)인 경우

trans-unit.source: A member of the array is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: 배열의 멤버가 null 참조(Visual Basic의 경우 <see langword="Nothing" />)인 경우입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> object to add to this collection.

The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.AddRange(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection)" /> method adds a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> object to the current collection.
<paramref name="controlCollection" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="controlCollection" />이 null 참조(Visual Basic의 경우 <see langword="Nothing" />)인 경우

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object for which to search.

The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.Contains(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl)" /> method determines whether this <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> object contains a specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.Contains(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl)" /> 메서드는 이 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> 개체에 지정된 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> 개체가 포함되어 있는지 여부를 확인합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object is part of the collection; <see langword="false" />, otherwise.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> 개체가 컬렉션에 포함되어 있으면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: A one-dimensional array that is the destination of the elements copied from the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> object.
The zero-based index of <c>array</c> where copying begins.

The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.CopyTo(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl[],System.Int32)" /> method copies the entire collection to a one-dimensional array, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.CopyTo(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl[],System.Int32)" /> 메서드는 대상 배열의 지정된 인덱스에서 시작하여 1차원 배열에 전체 컬렉션을 복사합니다.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="array" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" />이 null 참조(Visual Basic의 경우 <see langword="Nothing" />)인 경우

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero.
<paramref name="array" /> is multidimensional
-or-

The number of elements in the source <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> is greater than the available space from <paramref name="index" /> to the end of the destination <paramref name="array" />.
trans-unit.target: 소스 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" />의 요소 수가 대상 <paramref name="array" />의 <paramref name="index" />부터 끝까지 사용 가능한 공간보다 큽니다.

trans-unit.source: The type of the source <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> cannot be cast automatically to the type of the destination <paramref name="array" />.
trans-unit.target: 소스 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" />의 형식을 대상 <paramref name="array" />의 형식으로 자동 캐스팅할 수 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object for which the index is returned.

The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.IndexOf(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl)" /> method returns the zero-based index of the first occurrence of the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object in the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.IndexOf(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl)" /> 메서드는 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" />에 지정된 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> 개체에서 맨 처음 발견되는 0부터 시작하는 인덱스를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: The index value of the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object, if found; otherwise, -1.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> 개체가 있으면 이 개체의 인덱스 값이고, 그렇지 않으면 -1입니다.

trans-unit.source: The index in the collection at which to insert the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object.
The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object to be inserted into the collection.

The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.Insert(System.Int32,System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl)" /> method inserts the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object into the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.Insert(System.Int32,System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl)" /> 메서드는 지정된 인덱스에서 지정된 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> 개체를 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" />에 삽입합니다.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="value" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="value" />이 null 참조(Visual Basic의 경우 <see langword="Nothing" />)인 경우

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero, or <paramref name="index" /> is greater than the number of elements in the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> object.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" />가 0보다 작거나 <paramref name="index" />가 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> 개체의 요소 수보다 큰 경우

trans-unit.source: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> is read-only, or <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> has a fixed size.
The index value of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object.

The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.Item(System.Int32)" /> property contains the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.Item(System.Int32)" /> 속성은 지정된 인덱스에 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> 개체를 포함하고 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Contains the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object at the specified index.
There was an attempt to set the property to <see langword="null" />.
The object to evaluate.

The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.OnValidate(System.Object)" /> method verifies that <paramref name="value" /> is a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object.
This method does not return a value.
Instead, an exception is thrown if the specified object is null or is not a valid <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl> object.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 된 개체가 null 이거나 잘못 된 경우 예외가 throw 되는 대신, <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="value" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="value" />이 null 참조(Visual Basic의 경우 <see langword="Nothing" />)인 경우

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="value" /> is not a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object.
The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object to remove.

The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.Remove(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl)" /> method removes the first occurrence of the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object from the collection.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.Remove(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl)" /> 메서드는 컬렉션에서 첫 번째 지정된 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> 개체를 제거합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> is read-only, or <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> has a fixed size.
